Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done checking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Yatsufusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good. I think it'll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth asking Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Examination period for applicants\Nto be apprentice court herbalists...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so it was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.07,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been getting antsy\Nthinking about this for a while, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This path that I've started walking on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what shape,\Nwhat color, what smell it'll have?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can learn something today\Nthat I did not know yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be heading to the orientation\Nroom once all the examinees arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.43,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 4: From the Small Hand,\Na Burgeoning Concerto Resonates"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna walk around over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the court herbalist\NI saw at the pharmacy the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A compound for suppressing coughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, he'd still need\Nrainbow leaf and koko grass, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I still need rainbow leaf and\Nkoko grass, but it's not time to pick them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go pick them right after the sun rises,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,when the medicinal properties\Nare at their most effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When the medicinal properties\Nare at their most effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know when that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's knowledge that people who lived\Nin nature took a long time to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no classification\Nfor it in medical literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought it was important, so I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I can beat the people who\Nspent time studying with the actual plants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I can learn about living medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to take your\Ntest, right? Are you calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "kind of"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the chief herbalist\Nat Wistal Castle, Garak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The exam will look at your ability to\Nmanage herb gardens and medicine storage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,as that is what the work of court herbalist\Napprentices mainly consists of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be responsible for a small\Nmedicinal herb garden in the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,tending to and protecting the\Nenvironment and plants inside the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After two days, there will be an inspection,\Nand after that, you will submit a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all. Read the documents\Ngiven to you for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They use aqueducts to bring\Nthe water to all parts of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of them, but it's\Nmy first time seeing them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very efficient!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's some dirt in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw some lights on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even dawn yet...\NWhat is she doing by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait! Don't come this way--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wha...?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're locked in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who'd do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone call you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I'm in the middle of my\Ncourt herbalist apprentice exam right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So they did this knowing that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:07:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be an inspection in the morning,\Nso someone will let us out if we wait until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If word gets out that you were with me\Nin the middle of your test, it'll be bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But Zen, did you come here for a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I just... wandered over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, you smile and evade the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I had the chance to be\Nin such a well-maintained herb garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This plant should bloom facing upward\Nfrom late at night until morning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's water flowing underneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no irregularities in its environment,\Nbut the flowers seem listless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is sweet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The water around here is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There are toxins in the aqueducts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's fine. It doesn't affect humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... sure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What about the poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Of the toxins that\Nmedicinal herbs and plants carry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them tastes like honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's been mixed in with the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the plant with that toxin isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the water on top is fine,\Nis it somewhere on the bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,An herb that would make that toxin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what if this isn't\Nakegi shigure, but {\i1}yura{\i0} shigure...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If the roots are sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two types, yura and akegi, and it's\Nhard to tell the difference before they flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This yura plant was raised in\Nthe environment for akegi to flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was planted in the wrong way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If yura are raised in the wrong environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't flower but will\Nmake toxins in their roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is flowing into the\Naqueducts from the soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the yura and\Nthe other plants will wither and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen! Close the aqueduct\Nfrom here to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dig these out and replant them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right? If I help,\Nit might affect your exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll do whatever\NI can that's necessary right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't narrow your path?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided on a path where\NI could be Zen's ally in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't lose sight\Nof my path, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a guidepost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've received so much strength\Nto face forward from you, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that's so like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow leaf and koko grass...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in the garden, your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it so the yura shigure would flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been mistakenly planted as akegi shigure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You replanted all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You replanted the others, as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure they would not be\Naffected by the remaining toxins in the aqueducts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this in one night...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you had the prince help you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are important herbs\Nthat may save the prince someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an examinee who\Nwas mistaken for a prowler last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so that person must have locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to force someone\Nout of the competition, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness, will you leave\Nthe resolution of this matter to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The person was wearing a long coat\Nwith hair down to the waist tied back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you should also be aware there is a time\Nand place for your friendship with the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I came here on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, your status is such that\Nyour actions cannot be called into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With a single word, your friend could be\Naccepted unconditionally as a court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can try that if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl will never come\Nback to the castle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to anger her voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. What do you think\Nabout Shirayuki, Yatsufusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She passes with no complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, Shirayuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:13:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we officially accept you as\Nan apprentice court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The exam this time was\Nnot just tending the gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also to see if you could spot\Nthe difference between yura and akegi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been fine if you had\Njust noticed and wrote it in the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think anyone would\Nactually replant the whole garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu will sure be surprised\Nwhen he hears about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who thought of this test,\Nour youngest court herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Have you met him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we have Ryu\Nbe your supervisor, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chief Garak, there is something\NI would like your permission for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have passed the exam\Nto become apprentice court herbalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Higata, please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shirayuki, who will\Nbe your assistant from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She did an excellent job of clearing that test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'm Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything you don't\Nunderstand, just ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, please get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My name is Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ryu, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to call me sir.\NOr speak so formally to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, but... I am here to be taught by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a kid. It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will just stop using "sir," Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryu. Um... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow leaf and koko grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered them when their medicinal\Nproperties are at their most effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because it was very shocking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was such a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll grind them, so will you put in the\Nrainbow leaf and koko grass, in that order?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I've been feeling queasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to give me some\Nmedicine I can take right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Ryu, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That patient would be better off with\Nmedicine from the Chief or one of the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness... I'm too scared\Nto take medicine from that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it cause problems for you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, all he does is research plant poisons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's always looking\Nfor test subjects, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that I'd rather not\Nget involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that the toxins created by plants\Nto protect themselves from outside enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,are often used as medicines for humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But there may or may not have been victims--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can talk about\Nwith such groundless judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take that back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get so worked up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say foolish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get the chief herbalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Foolish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the first time\Nsomeone's said that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason,\NI don't really understand people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because my comprehension is beyond\Nwhat people normally attribute to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know if she's mad or not,\Nit would be quickest to just ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in Shirayuki's case,\NI recommend facing her straight on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't a child, I wouldn't\Ngive you advice like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's time for practice. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, once you finish the records\Nfor the patient just now, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Prince Zen's medical history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it out on my own judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you are with him the\Nmost out of all the court herbalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look to help you deal with emergencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the sake of your resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This part is all medication for injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A scratch from sword practice, and a sprain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A bruise from falling off the\Ncastle wall in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was he on the wall...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, age 13. Poisoning symptoms\Nand their progression?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A record of the administration of poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,February 5th. Seven hours after\Nadministration, he broke out in a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There was some shallow\Ndisturbance to his breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but no abnormalities in his speech or conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stable for 31 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,May 11th. Right after administration,\Nhe had difficulty walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Called for antidote three hours later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,July 1st. Thirty minutes after administration,\Nhe broke out in a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...with stabbing pains all over his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been building up an immunity to poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I thought I had to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut she's... crying... by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to look this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here until you're done\Nlooking at it. Okay, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Zen. Looks like I scared you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just... make you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if you call me by my name,\NI'll tell you if I'm mad or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in Shirayuki's case,\NI recommend facing her straight on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh... Shira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shira... yu... ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, thanks for running for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura shigure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the flower that was on the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the medicinal herbs,\Nyou like yura shigure, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's pretty and red.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura shigure. I'm the only one who\Ndoesn't know what kind of flower that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.78,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see it together sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can learn something today\Nthat I did not know yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside me, or someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding one thing and picking it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The bitter and the sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All in order to know the name of that flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it really was an evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you have to\Nthink of your own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I can leave by\Nmyself after calling you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I follow her for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:20.16,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 5: This Path,\Nthe Crystallization of Premonition"
